# Licensing

This repository contains packages under different licenses.

## AGPL-3.0-or-later

All packages under `anchr/` are licensed under the
[GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 or later](https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html).
See `anchr/website/LICENSE` for the full text.

## MIT

All packages under `shared/` and `november-sierra/` are licensed under the
[MIT License](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT).
See the `LICENSE` file in each package for the full text.

---

Each workspace package contains its own `LICENSE` file. When in doubt, check the
`license` field in the package's `package.json`.
